- Colorscale can be set automatically 

- beside grafical output produce numerical count of voxels by map regions

-- combine those tables of numerical count by anatomical regions (add GM/WM, up/down and atlas column)

- and then create some plots in R

-- od istega avtorja se ne smejo podvajat!

-- če delam s kroglami in iterativno večam, bi moral kontrolirat še, da ne preskoči krogla na drug girus (use clustering)

- make a select box, to select the template you want

-- then use afni/SUMA volume and surface templates https://afni.nimh.nih.gov/pub/dist/doc/program_help/suma.html


